In you fellowship draw as many cards as you can, set your deck up and move. Then you heal Legolas and Gimli or Tharin. Use your archers to shoot down your enimes and usually dircet archery with Legolas. There will probably be one or two minions left then Gimli and Tharin to fight. Simple, right.  Elrond can heal Grimir and Tharin and they heal Legolas.<br>
